OL,3,CBacklash after council axes hundreds
OL,4,Cof gritting routes
OL,6,FResidents say a decision by Calderdale
OL,7,FCouncil to axe some winter gritting
OL,8,Froutes to save money could have
OL,9,F"terrible" consequences.
OL,11,FThe council announced last month that
OL,12,Fit would reduce the number of
OL,13,Fprecautionary gritting routes it
OL,14,Fcovered to save #300,000 from its
OL,15,F#1.7million winter services budget.
OL,17,FThe new programme will not come into
OL,18,Feffect until December.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
