OL,3,CBacklash after council axes hundreds
OL,4,Cof gritting routes
OL,6,FBut, ahead of predicted snowy and icy
OL,7,Fconditions overnight on Tuesday, some
OL,8,Fof those living on affected roads say
OL,9,Fthey could be left stranded and fear
OL,10,Fserious accidents could happen.
OL,12,FMichelle Polczynski, who lives in
OL,13,FBrighouse, said: "It's going to have a
OL,14,Fmajor effect. There's people taking
OL,15,Ftheir children to school. There will
OL,16,Fbe absolute uproar once it happens.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
