OL,3,CBacklash after council axes hundreds
OL,4,Cof gritting routes
OL,6,F"If they are not gritted, people are
OL,7,Fgoing to end up falling. There are
OL,8,Fgoing to end up being cars sliding
OL,9,Fdown and crashing. It's going to
OL,10,Fabsolutely terrible.
OL,12,F"We pay council tax and gritting does
OL,13,Fcome into it. The council have a duty
OL,14,Fof care to the public. This is not a
OL,15,Fduty of care to us in Brighouse."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
