OL,3,CBacklash after council axes hundreds
OL,4,Cof gritting routes
OL,6,FThe Labour-run council said it had
OL,7,Fprioritised busy roads, routes needed
OL,8,Fby emergency services and roads that
OL,9,Fprovide access to community facilities
OL,10,Fsuch as hospitals, schools and town
OL,11,Fcentres.
OL,13,FBut hundreds of other streets will not
OL,14,Fbe routinely gritted. Signs have been
OL,15,Finstalled in affected areas.
OL,17,FMs Polczynski said: "You can't really
OL,18,Fpostpone going to work, because you've
OL,19,Fgot to go to work.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
