OL,3,CBacklash after council axes hundreds
OL,4,Cof gritting routes
OL,6,F"I was quite annoyed to think a road
OL,7,Fthat is not getting gritted is the
OL,8,Froad I use to go to work every
OL,9,Fmorning. Obviously, it's quite a steep
OL,10,Fhill and we won't be able to get down.
OL,12,F"To use the bus, then I would have to
OL,13,Fwalk down, so I would end up falling,
OL,14,Flike many people would if they don't
OL,15,Fgo in their cars."
OL,17,FAnother resident, Andrew Tagg
OL,18,Fcriticised the council's decision-
OL,19,Fmaking process, saying the types of
OL,20,Froad surfaces and local knowledge have
OL,21,Fnot been considered.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
