OL,3,CBacklash after council axes hundreds
OL,4,Cof gritting routes
OL,6,FAmong the roads affected is Brackenbed
OL,7,FLane, which Mr Tagg said could become
OL,8,F"a death trap".
OL,10,FHe described the road as a "rat run"
OL,11,Fwith considerable amounts of traffic
OL,12,Fand said it should be classed as a
OL,13,Fprimary route.
OL,15,FMr Tagg labelled it a "negligent
OL,16,Fpolicy".
OL,18,FThe concern comes as the Met Office
OL,19,Fhas issued a yellow weather warning
OL,20,Ffor snow and ice overnight on Tuesday.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
