OL,3,CBacklash after council axes hundreds
OL,4,Cof gritting routes
OL,6,FBut the council's cabinet member for
OL,7,Ftransport, Cllr Sarah Courtney, said
OL,8,Fthe council was targeting resources
OL,9,Fwhere they were needed most.
OL,11,FShe advised that everyone should
OL,12,Fconsider how to prepare for the winter
OL,13,Fto stay safe, such as checking public
OL,14,Ftransport or postponing a trip until
OL,15,Fthe weather improves.
OL,17,FShe said: "The geography of our
OL,18,Fborough, with its mix of rural
OL,19,Fcommunities and towns, means that it's
OL,20,Fnot possible for us to grit every
OL,21,Fstreet and road."
